      "metadata": "{\"source\":\"memos-primary\",\"memo_name\":\"memos/CgiZNnhgKqrBxJsaxvxFy7\",\"memo_uid\":\"CgiZNnhgKqrBxJsaxvxFy7\",\"memo_update_time\":\"2026-03-14T14:02:24Z\"}"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab42bc-6193-58af-8710-28debbd591de",
      "text": "Ollama API error 400: {\"error\":\"registry.ollama.ai/library/my-qwen:latest does not support tools\"} 通过飞书发消息，结果反馈以上文字，帮我修复一下。",
      "category": "fact",
      "scope": "agent:main",
